Method Detail

getGraphics

public abstract Graphics getGraphics()
Enabled: Gets a Graphics object that will draw to the next page. The page is sent to the printer when the graphics object is disposed. This graphics object will also implement the PrintGraphics interface.

See Also:
PrintGraphics

getPageDimension

public abstract Dimension getPageDimension()
Enabled: Returns the dimensions of the page in pixels. The resolution of the page is chosen so that it is similar to the screen resolution.

getPageResolution

public abstract int getPageResolution()
Enabled: Returns the resolution of the page in pixels per inch. Note that this doesn't have to correspond to the physical resolution of the printer.

lastPageFirst

public abstract boolean lastPageFirst()
Enabled: Returns true if the last page will be printed first.
